We have a fully stocked tackle shop  specializing in float fishing including egg sacs, rods, reels, etc.  We offer fish cleaning and smoking, possibly the best smoked fish in New York!  The Salmon River Tavern Restaurant features breakfast, lunch and dinner menus prepared by our own Culinary Institute of America  graduate.  Any meal can be boxed “to go!”  Selections range from the most  popular hearty egg sandwich breakfast & waffles to the best  ”any style” burgers in town. And don’t forget our famous pulled pork sandwiches, our “new” cheese steak sandwiches and Walts’ homemade chili! We offer guide service and lake charters.  We are situated on ATV and Snowmobile trails and don’t forget we provide lodging!  Rooms are unique with private baths, some with river views and some with private kitchens. Relax by the fire, play darts, have a drink and talk to other fisherman at the end of the day in our guest lounge!  It is best to call in advance for room reservations.  Keep in mind that  when you stay at our lodge you are in a “walk to” location, walk to food, tackle and the river!  So you won’t need your car once you get here!  We look forward to seeing you here at Salmon River Outfitters where we always strive to make your visit a pleasurable and memorable one!

Full Description: In November 2016, Mayor Steve Adler announced the formation of the Task Force on Institutional Racism & Systemic Inequities (IRSI) comprised of several local representatives from business, education, housing, health, and criminal justice to address institutional racism in Austin. The task force members formed five working groups to focus in key areas: Education; Real Estate & Housing; Health; Finance, Banking, & Industry; and Civil & Criminal Justice. Mayor Adler asked Dr. Colette Pierce Burnette, Huston-Tillotson University President, and Dr. Paul Cruz, Austin ISD Superintendent, to lead the effort in collaboration with over 200 community members. Collectively, the task force developed 278 recommendations that would attempt to create transparency in law enforcement, provide funding for housing inequalities, and provide a path to review Austin’s governmental policies that may perpetuate the systemic inequities among many others.

Description: MeetingMogul app offers one-touch dialing into any conference call from a user’s smartphone, collaboration, and cost-saving features.
Headquarters Regions: San Francisco Bay Area, Silicon Valley, West Coast
Full Description: MeetingMogul allows you to join any conference call with one-touch, you won’t ever have to remember or enter phone numbers and audio pins to dial into conference calls again.  No more fumbling with your iPhone on the go! MeetingMogul works with all conference call providers including WebEx, Skype for Business, GoToMeeting, Join.Me and validates each dial-in number before your call to ensure seamless connectivity. Over 150,000 conference calls made! Used by executives at Microsoft, Johnson & Johnson, IBM, Teradata, Deloitte, T-Mobile, AT&T, Deutsche Bank, VMWare, Xerox, Jaguar Land Rover, Accenture, UPS and many more! HOW IT WORKS: • MeetingMogul parses your iPhone calendar(s) and shows all upcoming conference calls and meetings in a convenient agenda view.  • MeetingMogul detects your upcoming call events and notifies you in advance. • Simply touching the call icon or acting on the reminder will dial you right into your conference call, without having to look up, remember or dial any numbers.  • MeetingMogul lets you stay on top of your meetings by easily creating an Agenda and Follow-ups right on your iPhone and sharing them with all meeting participants. KEY FEATURES: * Easy one-touch mobile conference calling: Say goodbye to ever changing dial-in numbers and long passcodes. * All Meetings in One Place: The app syncs all active calendar events at launch and displays them in a clean and simple Agenda view. * Note Sharing: The app allows for collaborative note sharing between all meeting participants. * Smart Dialing Wizard: Ability to edit the dialing sequence using the Dial Sequence Editing Wizard. * Adding Favorites Bridges: Frequently used bridges can be saved for easy dialing and instant creation of new conference calls and meetings. * CRM Integration: Offers Salesforce and NetSuite calendar integration. * Send Notifications: Notify meeting & conference call participants with a single tap, via email or SMS (using predefined & custom messages). * Reach out features: Call any meeting participant instantly from the app. * Apple watch support - join conference calls, receive and send notifications right from your wrist! * Calling Card Integration: Dial contacts and conference calls using calling cards to save cost while traveling. * Recording Notes: Voice notes can be recorded against recently concluded calls, these are automatically saved on the app. * Data Security: All location, calendar, contacts, host data and pass codes are stored on the device

Description: Paradigm Select Assets is an asset fund for investment in distressed debt.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Los Angeles Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Paradigm Select Assets is an asset fund for investment in distressed debt.The purpose of the fund is to deliver consistently high returns that are uncorrelated to the equity markets.Paradigm purchases under performing debt, assetizes the debt claims into legal judgments, and then liquidates the portfolios on the secondary market. Their “Recovery Valuation Approach” utilizes proprietary methods, as well as comprehensive financial models based upon $2B of processed debt history, to uncover value niches for investment in the credit markets. The Opportunity: Paradigm Select Assets has positioned itself for a unique opportunity in the debt buying arena. Two recent factors have combined to dramatically bring down prices of debt portfolios, while at the same time making larger quantities of high quality debt available on the market. Banks are charging off business and consumer loans earlier than a year ago, and this has resulted in higher availability of fresh debt paper. Also, the tightening of credit terms has forced several larger debt buyers onto the sidelines, bringing down prices of charged off debt to the lowest levels seen in the last 10 years. The reduction of prices by more than 50% from a year ago has created a unique buying opportunity in the market.

It was a time of "trial and error" but now we are confident to say that our mulch, compost and enriched topsoil is the best in the Kansas City area.   Today, Lawn-Corps owns and operates a 37 acre yard waste processing facility in Belton, Missouri. They have become the only green waste hauler in South Kansas City that collects and processes yard waste into high quality products such as compost and organic mulches.
